abstract: Stocks fall modestly to end quiet week; oil prices end rally.
lead_paragraph: Oil prices rose but have not managed to break out of a range. Energy stocks sputtered, though tech shares posted small advances.

headline.main: Wall St. Closes Lower as Hopes for Oil Rally Fade
